<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>About Me</strong></p>
</div>
<hr />
<p>Hello, I exist!</p>
<p>I discovered this site in 2016, and I joined in 2017, only getting invested in the later half of the year. I'm not really much of a writer, so I decided to post some of my pixel art. People liked it, so I made an art page, then I updated my art style a few times, then you started reading this.</p>
<p>My pixel art used to look like solid-colored blobs, but I've since developed a more refined and cartoony art style. That's not to say it's my only style, though; I have an enormous amount of sprite work for mods that I'll never get around to making.</p>
<hr />
